posts.title: Mango Man on the J got off at Gates Ave. alongside me - missed connections
posts.body: You were wearing a Mango Man leather jacket and had a black rolling bag. I was the woman wearing a tank top & grey jeans and was balancing a bag between my legs. Stood by the door behind you. We both got off at Gates Ave, and even walked side by side towards the exit. Noticed some good energy there and wished I had said something.
